## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src) =>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
        let img = new Image();
        img.src = src;
        img.onload = () => {
            resolve(img)
        }
        img.onerror = () => {
            reject(new Error("error"))
        }

    })
}
